{"article_id":"vYW5EV4NXcVO4HY3","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"HANOI -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"President Donald Trump opened an historic second summit with Kim Jong Un here Wednesday","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"by pledging to push for North Korean denuclearization ,","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"even as he faced a political firestorm at home","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"that threatens to eclipse any progress .","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"`` I think","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"it 'll be very successful , ''","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"Trump said","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"as he and Kim posed for the cameras ,","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"proclaiming","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"that he and his North Korean counterpart have a `` great relationship . '' At another photo opportunity , Kim said","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"he is certain of an outcome","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"``","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"that will be welcomed by all people , ''","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"and `` I will do my best","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"to make that happen . ''","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"But Trump 's diplomatic efforts come","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"as his former personal attorney , Michael Cohen , is expected to allege `` criminal conduct '' by the president in his first public testimony later Wednesday before Congress .","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"Trump met with Kim for a brief private conversation ,","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"followed by a `` social dinner , ''","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"all marking their first face-to-face encounter","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"since the two met in Singapore last summer .","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"The ceremonial events ,","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"splashed across U.S. television screens early Wednesday morning ,","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"are expected give way to more substantive talks on the second and final day of the summit Thursday .","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"Simply put , Trump is trying to get Kim to commit to specific steps","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"to eliminate nuclear weapons programs ,","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"while Kim wants Trump to lift economic sanctions","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"that are crippling his impoverished nation .","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"In urging denuclearization ,","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"Trump told Kim","depth":12},{"id":31,"text":"that","depth":12},{"id":32,"text":"`` some people would like to see it go quicker ,","depth":13},{"id":33,"text":"but you 're satisfied ,","depth":14},{"id":34,"text":"I 'm satisfied . ''","depth":14},{"id":35,"text":"He also suggested","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"giving up nuclear weapons would draw economic assistance ,","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"telling Kim","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"that North Korea has `` unbelievable , unlimited potential , ''","depth":13},{"id":39,"text":"and `` I look forward to watching it happen","depth":14},{"id":40,"text":"and to helping it to happen . ''","depth":14},{"id":41,"text":"Asked about another goal","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"- formally ending the Korean War -","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"Trump told reporters ,","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"`` we 'll see . ''","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"Meanwhile , Trump and other White House officials ,","depth":13},{"id":46,"text":"mindful","depth":14},{"id":47,"text":"that the visit to Vietnam is competing for public attention among millions of Americans ,","depth":14},{"id":48,"text":"attacked Cohen in the hours before the Kim meeting .","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"Trump tweeted","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"that Cohen `` did bad things","depth":14},{"id":51,"text":"unrelated to Trump , ''","depth":14},{"id":52,"text":"and `` is lying","depth":14},{"id":53,"text":"in order to reduce his prison time . ''","depth":14},{"id":54,"text":"Some foreign policy analysts said","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"they worry","depth":13},{"id":56,"text":"that Trump will be too willing to strike a bad deal with Kim","depth":14},{"id":57,"text":"in order to draw attention from his domestic problems ,","depth":15},{"id":58,"text":"including Cohen 's testimony .","depth":15},{"id":59,"text":"`` Congress should have postponed Cohen testimony ,","depth":13},{"id":60,"text":"and Potus should not be tweeting about Cohen from Hanoi , ''","depth":13},{"id":61,"text":"tweeted Richard Haass , president of the Council on Foreign Relations .","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"Trump appeared annoyed","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"when reporters asked him about Cohen at one of the summit photo opps .","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"The White House later restricted reporter access to the dinner with Trump , Kim , and their aides .","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"The president did say","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"he plans to hold a news conference after Thursday 's meetings with the North Korean leader .","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"Trump also spent some pre-meeting time","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"launching a Twitter attack on one of his congressional critics , Sen. Richard Blumenthal , D-Conn. ,","depth":13},{"id":69,"text":"and claiming","depth":14},{"id":70,"text":"he discussed the senator 's exaggerations about his war record in a meeting with Vietnam officials .","depth":14},{"id":71,"text":"Tweeting","depth":14},{"id":72,"text":"that `` I have now spent more time in Vietnam than Da Nang Dick Blumenthal , ''","depth":14},{"id":73,"text":"Trump added","depth":14},{"id":74,"text":"that `` his war stories of his heroism in Vietnam were a total fraud","depth":16},{"id":75,"text":"- he was never even there .","depth":16},{"id":76,"text":"We talked about it today with Vietnamese leaders ! ''","depth":15},{"id":77,"text":"Trump did not serve in the military during the Vietnam years ,","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"claiming college and medical deferments","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"that included bone spurs in his foot .","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"The tumult back in Washington","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"- lawmakers are also busy with a measure ,","depth":14},{"id":82,"text":"approved by the Democratic-controlled House ,","depth":14},{"id":83,"text":"to repeal Trump 's border wall emergency -","depth":13},{"id":84,"text":"threaten to overshadow the work in Hanoi .","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"The president 's troubles only add to the pressure","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"to deliver results with Kim ,","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"who has signaled an interest in stronger relations with the United States","depth":13},{"id":88,"text":"but declined to dismantle his nuclear program .","depth":13},{"id":89,"text":"In the days","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"leading up to the summit ,","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"Trump appeared to lower expectations ,","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"claiming","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"he is `` in no rush '' for denuclearization","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"as long as Pyongyang continues to suspend missile tests .","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"Hours before the sit-down with the North Korean leader , Trump held largely ceremonial meetings with the leaders of Vietnam ,","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"and said","depth":13},{"id":97,"text":"their country can be a model for Kim ,","depth":14},{"id":98,"text":"whom he described as `` my friend . ''","depth":14},{"id":99,"text":"`` Vietnam is thriving like few places on earth .","depth":14},{"id":100,"text":"North Korea would be the same , and very quickly ,","depth":15},{"id":101,"text":"if it would denuclearize , ''","depth":15},{"id":102,"text":"Trump tweeted early in the day .","depth":13},{"id":103,"text":"More than four decades after the Vietnam War , the Vietnamese view the summit as an opportunity","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"to assert themselves on the world diplomatic stage .","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"Heavily promoting the Trump-Kim summit ,","depth":11},{"id":106,"text":"light poles in Hanoi are festooned with the flags of the U.S. , North Korea and Vietnam ,","depth":12},{"id":107,"text":"mounted on a shield","depth":13},{"id":108,"text":"featuring an image of a handshake .","depth":13},{"id":109,"text":"Large posters","depth":12},{"id":110,"text":"advertising the summit","depth":12},{"id":111,"text":"proclaim Hanoi as `` The City For Peace . ''","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"Raising the curtain :","depth":8},{"id":113,"text":"Trump-Kim summit :","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"What happened at their first meeting","depth":10},{"id":115,"text":"- and what to expect at their next","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"The demands :","depth":8},{"id":117,"text":"Trump-Kim summit :","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"North Korea must do something 'meaningful '","depth":11},{"id":119,"text":"to denuclearize","depth":11},{"id":120,"text":"before sanctions relief","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"Trump and Kim met at the Sofitel Legend Metropole Hotel , an Art Nouveau masterpiece","depth":10},{"id":122,"text":"that harkens back to French colonial days in Hanoi .","depth":10},{"id":123,"text":"Past guests at the hotel have ranged from the comedian Charlie Chaplin to current Russian President Vladimir Putin .","depth":9},{"id":124,"text":"A one-of-a-kind relationship :","depth":10},{"id":125,"text":"Trump-Kim summit :","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"From fire and fury to love letters , not your traditional relationship","depth":9},{"id":127,"text":"Trump and aides have demanded","depth":9},{"id":128,"text":"that North Korea identify and destroy facilities","depth":10},{"id":129,"text":"used to make nuclear weapons .","depth":10},{"id":130,"text":"Kim , however , believes","depth":9},{"id":131,"text":"denuclearization should cover the entire region","depth":10},{"id":132,"text":"- including U.S. weapons systems","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"designed to protect ally South Korea .","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"Kim says","depth":10},{"id":135,"text":"he will not take major steps toward denuclearization","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"until the United States and other countries lift at least some of the sanctions","depth":12},{"id":137,"text":"that have crippled North Korea 's economy .","depth":12},{"id":138,"text":"Trump has said","depth":11},{"id":139,"text":"sanctions will not be removed","depth":12},{"id":140,"text":"until Kim starts to denuclearize ,","depth":12},{"id":141,"text":"though he has also held out the possibility of other economic assistance .","depth":10},{"id":142,"text":"The economy is one of the reasons","depth":10},{"id":143,"text":"the U.S. agreed to meet in Vietnam .","depth":10},{"id":144,"text":"It hopes","depth":10},{"id":145,"text":"North Korea will follow the model of its communist ally ,","depth":11},{"id":146,"text":"which developed a quasi-capitalist sector after economic reforms in the 1980s .","depth":11},{"id":147,"text":"Follow the money :","depth":5},{"id":148,"text":"Trump-Kim summit :","depth":6},{"id":149,"text":"Trump hints at rewards for North Korea","depth":6},{"id":150,"text":"While neither leader is expected to open an embassy in the other 's country ,","depth":6},{"id":151,"text":"negotiators are discussing `` liaison offices ''","depth":7},{"id":152,"text":"that could be used","depth":8},{"id":153,"text":"to improve communications between the two governments .","depth":8},{"id":154,"text":"Trump has been open to a treaty","depth":7},{"id":155,"text":"to formally end the Korean War ,","depth":8},{"id":156,"text":"which is technically ongoing","depth":9},{"id":157,"text":"even though hostilities were suspended with an armistice in 1953 .","depth":9},{"id":158,"text":"Negotiators are working on what aides called a `` peace declaration , '' a non-binding political statement","depth":7},{"id":159,"text":"to affirm","depth":8},{"id":160,"text":"North and South Korea are no longer at war .","depth":8},{"id":161,"text":"The history :","depth":5},{"id":162,"text":"How the North and South negotiated a truce in Korean War","depth":5},{"id":163,"text":"Sung-Yoon Lee , a Korea expert with the Fletcher School at Tufts University , said","depth":8},{"id":164,"text":"Kim wants to do just enough","depth":11},{"id":165,"text":"to satisfy Trump","depth":11},{"id":166,"text":"- `` like retiring an exhausted nuclear site","depth":11},{"id":167,"text":"he no longer needs '' -","depth":11},{"id":168,"text":"while retaining a weapons program","depth":10},{"id":169,"text":"he depends on for survival .","depth":10},{"id":170,"text":"`` Two steps forward and one step back is still progress for North Korea , ''","depth":8},{"id":171,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":172,"text":"Olivia Enos , a policy analyst with the Asian Studies Center at The Heritage Foundation in Washington , said","depth":8},{"id":173,"text":"she hopes","depth":9},{"id":174,"text":"Trump and his team tread cautiously .","depth":9},{"id":175,"text":"Give too much ,","depth":10},{"id":176,"text":"she said ,","depth":10},{"id":177,"text":"and the U.S. will lose its leverage","depth":10},{"id":178,"text":"and get little in return .","depth":10},{"id":179,"text":"`` The president 's willingness","depth":11},{"id":180,"text":"to compromise","depth":11},{"id":181,"text":"threatens to undermine the administration 's maximum pressure strategy","depth":11},{"id":182,"text":"that brought Kim Jong Un to the negotiating table in the first place , ''","depth":11},{"id":183,"text":"she said .","depth":9},{"id":184,"text":"While analysts worried","depth":7},{"id":185,"text":"that Trump might give up too much to Kim ,","depth":7},{"id":186,"text":"Cohen planned to mention the president 's Vietnam trip in his testimony .","depth":7},{"id":187,"text":"In a prepared statement","depth":11},{"id":188,"text":"first reported late Tuesday by Politico ,","depth":11},{"id":189,"text":"Cohen cited the deferments","depth":11},{"id":190,"text":"Trump received during the Vietnam War .","depth":11},{"id":191,"text":"`` 'You think","depth":12},{"id":192,"text":"I 'm stupid ,","depth":12},{"id":193,"text":"I was n't going to Vietnam , ' ''","depth":11},{"id":194,"text":"Cohen quotes Trump as saying .","depth":10},{"id":195,"text":"In his prepared testimony , Cohen adds :","depth":9},{"id":196,"text":"`` I find it ironic , President Trump , that you are in Vietnam right now . ''","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":393,"left":0,"right":392,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":392,"left":342,"right":391,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":342,"left":213,"right":341,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":213,"left":200,"right":212,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":200,"left":1,"right":199,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":199,"left":2,"right":198,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":198,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":212,"left":210,"right":211,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":210,"left":203,"right":209,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":203,"left":201,"right":202,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":201,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":202,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":209,"left":204,"right":208,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":204,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":208,"left":206,"right":207,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":206,"left":11,"right":205,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":205,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":207,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":211,"left":16,"right":17,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":341,"left":219,"right":340,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":219,"left":216,"right":218,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":216,"left":214,"right":215,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":21